n: Honey, Mustard, and Yogurt Salad Dressing
des: "This dressing is a must-have because it makes all salads super-yummy. It's so simple! Top your salad with chicken with almonds, spinach and berries, or orange segments. Use your imagination!"
ins: Whisk together the yogurt, honey, mustard, and celery seed in a small bowl. Refrigerate at least 1 hour before serving.
